parameters: \n<Goblin1>Heh heh, look at those long-legs! They can't get to us!
\n<Goblin2>Keheheh! They're stupid! Like Krenko says! STOOPID!
\n<Goblin1>Try and reach us now! HAH! Let's call in the boys to clean these up!
\n<Zahin>Huh, I think I see a surface not too far down from here, maybe...
\n<Zahin>It's gonna be so cringe if I die from this.
\n<Goblin2>Must have felt shame at being outsmarted by our boss!
